{
  "stem": "21308.4",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I said, do you know where all your old man used to live and worked under you here?",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And he said, [GERMAN].",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I said, well, bugger off and find them, and bring them back in here.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And so he went off with this jeep, and came back with all these hands.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And then they were told by me, and in no uncertain fashion, that they wouldn't leave the camp until the water was running, and the emergency generators were working, and there was water going into the sewage.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And they were first class.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And I kept them in the camp for five days, and one of them said to me, well, you know, our wives will be getting very worried about us.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And so I said to Hubert Steinberg, I said, now, translate this very carefully.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I said, tell him to look around, and he'll see all the people here in this camp in this dreadful uniform.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And I said, there are a lot of women all over Europe worrying about what's happened to their people.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Don't tell me you're worried, because you're just a few, and your bloody government's caused all this trouble.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And so anyway, that shut him up.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "But they all worked very well, as Germans do.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "They worked well.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And then when after five days I let them go home, they lived inside the camp.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "They ate in the camp.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 7 SECONDS] We eventually got all the people into accommodation in the camp.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "Many of them sort of put themselves into accommodation.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "But of course, as I told you before, I asked my colonel if there was typhus in the camp, because we knew at Belson there was typhus.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And they laid it on on the 8th Corps very good.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
